HEADWORD: Hydrosoma
<hw>Hy`dro*so"ma</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. <ets>hydrosoma</ets>. See
<er>Hydra</er>, and <er>-some</er> body.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>All the zooids of a hydroid colony collectively, including the
nutritive and reproductive zooids, and often other kinds.</def>⟦br⟧
